issue.body:
***Note**: This issue was originally created as [ARROW-4555](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ARROW-4555). Please see the [migration documentation](https://gist.github.com/toddfarmer/12aa88361532d21902818a6044fda4c3) for further details.*

### Original Issue Description:
It'd be great to have a few high-level functions that implicitly create the Schema, RecordBatches, etc. from a Table and a list of Columns. For example:
```actionscript

const table = Table.new(
  Column.new('foo', ...),
  Column.new('bar', ...)
);
```
